ote>係咪練棍波？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 我男朋友都只係識自動波⋯</blockquote><br />\nhehe"},{"pid":"e017285009bdc5980c0c0ee9d016b630bb2ba39b","tid":290254,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你男朋友教車師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我男朋友揸車都好屎 <br />\n唔係囉 佢地只係唔熟既同事關係<br />\n但條女好似唔錯咁"},{"pid":"d2bd32d420ba7d020ba0a90ca74098469c03a49b","tid":290254,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕對唔比<br />\n你男朋友係都要話要去 既話<br />\n你就同佢講咁你都搵個男人練下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩唔熟都要搞我男朋友<br />\n係咪別有用心"},{"pid":"ecc43e83162a8aa4037ad61b6431e0ef9e214e31","tid":290254,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絕對唔比<br />\n你男朋友係都要話要去 既話<br />\n你就同佢講咁你都搵個男人練下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩唔熟都要搞我男朋友<br />\n係咪別有用心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明顯想收你條仔做兵"},{"pid":"f30db6829f8f0fdce1e72c797d087ec03dfa0236","tid":290254,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪練棍波？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 我男朋友都只係識自動波⋯</blockquote><br />\n你都識講，自動波啦"},{"pid":"4327005792f2cbe92354a5ed630351c76942fa3c","tid":290254,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絕對唔比<br />\n你男朋友係都要話要去 既話<br />\n你就同佢講咁你都搵個男人練下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩唔熟都要搞我男朋友<br />\n係咪別有用心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明顯想收你條仔做兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我男朋友又話想幫佢 即係佢做左兵？⋯⋯<br />\n有女朋友都做人隻兵 即係騎牛搵馬？"},{"pid":"3dad3c3581c1ec04e9e0081d95cc5296367aa96d","tid":290254,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,