"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絕對唔比<br />\n你男朋友係都要話要去 既話<br />\n你就同佢講咁你都搵個男人練下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩唔熟都要搞我男朋友<br />\n係咪別有用心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明顯想收你條仔做兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我男朋友又話想幫佢 即係佢做左兵？⋯⋯<br />\n有女朋友都做人隻兵 即係騎牛搵馬？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係果條女正過你。"},{"pid":"413a36f196041d83da1c79a52e4fbff6c3c7506c","tid":290254,"uid":75509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"想試下架<span style=\"color: red;\">車</span>可以有幾<span style=\"color: red;\">震</span>"},{"pid":"76e8da8368c5412a8608e01c73e11ae4d6216251","tid":290254,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想試下架<span style=\"color: red;\">車</span>可以有幾<span style=\"color: red;\">震</span></blockquote><br />\n仲有枝波棍實唔實淨"},{"pid":"8e76121a8f334dc57a4faacb416ef8fb790e9619","tid":290254,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"依d臭bitch"},{"pid":"3c5a5e9a9c059c6ec1d7d710a9626bde23b78c9f","tid":290254,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"想同你男朋友推車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b16ea799a8e2ac73f0f0f322d7855c85b3adfd","tid":290254,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"乜練車會有好多身體接觸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242bc715ddbb633bdbf2f20cfe402c1a9079d767","tid":290254,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:21:56.000Z","msg":"練下車輪姐，冇事嘅"}]}